    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Military groups of the Fante of Ghana, constituting the primary defensive units of the Fante states. They also serve political, social, and religious functions. They are widely known for the colorful flags that represent them at important festivals.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
